`LightStringGraph` includes some code taken from the following projects:

- `kseq.h` from the [`seqtk` project](https://github.com/lh3/seqtk) by
  Heng Li (and collaborators) released under the MIT license

`LightStringGraph` is intended to use with the results produced by
[`BEETL`](https://github.com/BEETL/BEETL), written by Bauer, Cox, Rosone
et al. and released under the "Illumina Non-Commercial Use Software and
Source Code License Agreement". A version modified by us in order to
compute the LCP is available at the [AlgoLab repository](https://github.com/AlgoLab/BEETL).
